title: Taco Amigo
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Re-opened Apr 2016 after renovations. Mexican cantina, seats 30+. Some items have vegan options, and many of the stable ingredients such as the rice, beans, and guacamole are vegan. Just ask. Directions: From Itaewon station go out exit 4, once at the top of the stairs, go down the street behind and to the left of the stairs you just came up, and it's on the right 50 feet up the street.
